<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Withdrawal Details</title>
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#0d0d0d">
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/favicon.png" type="image/png">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/remixicon@3.4.0/fonts/remixicon.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Luckiest+Guy&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/toastify-js/src/toastify.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/dashboard.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/payment.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/funding-details.css">
</head>

<body>

    <!-- ALL ABOUT LARGE SCREENS -->
    <%- include ('partials/big-screen') %>

    <div class="hold">

        <main class="main-content">

            <!-- Header -->
            <div class="header">
                <div class="brand-text">
                    <h1>Withdrawal Center</h1>
                    <a href="/profile">
                        <div class="back-icon">
                            <i class="ri-arrow-left-s-line"></i>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
            <div class="container">

                <div class="main">
                    <h1>Withdrawal Guide</h1>
                    <p>
                        Earn from your stores daily and withdraw easily. Here’s a simple step-by-step guide to make sure you never miss your earnings:
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="main-card">

                    <!-- Step 1 -->
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-number">1</div>
                        <h3 class="step-title">Daily Earnings from Your Store</h3>
                        <p class="step-description">
                            Once you purchase a store, it earns <strong>daily income</strong> until it expires. You can track your earnings per store in your profile. Earnings accumulate automatically.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Step 2 -->
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-number">2</div>
                        <h3 class="step-title">Claim When Eligible</h3>
                        <p class="step-description">
                            You can claim your earnings in the payout page anytime your store has reached the <strong>minimum threshold (₦1,000)</strong>. For expired stores, a <strong>Claim</strong> button section appears in the payout page for claiming.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Step 3 -->
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-number">3</div>
                        <h3 class="step-title">Provide Bank Details</h3>
                        <p class="step-description">
                            Claims require your bank details. Tap the <strong>settings icon</strong> on your profile to save <strong>Bank Name, Account Name, and Account Number</strong>. Claims cannot be submitted without these details.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Step 4 -->
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-number">4</div>
                        <h3 class="step-title">Submit Your Claim</h3>
                        <p class="step-description">
                            Click the <strong>Claim</strong> button for the store. The system sends your earnings to the admin for review. Each store must be claimed separately.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Step 5 -->
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-number">5</div>
                        <h3 class="step-title">Admin Approval</h3>
                        <p class="step-description">
                            Your claim is marked as <strong>Pending</strong>. Admin verifies the request and your bank details. You’ll be notified once approved or declined.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Step 6 -->
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-number">6</div>
                        <h3 class="step-title">Receive Payment</h3>
                        <p class="step-description">
                            When approved, the claimed amount is transferred to your account. The expired store is marked as <strong>claimed</strong>, and the Claim button disappears. Related stats for that store are reset.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Step 7 -->
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-number">7</div>
                        <h3 class="step-title">Referral & Rewards</h3>
                        <p class="step-description">
                            Your referral link remains active once you purchase a paid store. You can continue earning bonuses through referrals even after the store expires.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                </div>

                <!-- FOOTER SECTION -->
                <div class="information">

                    <div class="info-box">
                        <div class="info-title">Processing Time</div>
                        <p>
                            Most withdrawals are processed within <strong>24 hours</strong> after admin approval. Bank posting times may vary.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="warning-box">
                        <div class="warning-title">Security Notice</div>
                        <p>
                            Only withdraw to your own bank account. Never share login or OTP codes. Always confirm you are on the official website before submitting a claim.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="contact-section">
                        <div class="help">Need Help?</div>
                        <p>
                            If you cannot see the Claim button, your store may still be active. For issues with bank details or claims, contact our live chat, email, or Telegram support — available 24/7.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>

        </main>
    </div>

</body>

</html>
